Package architecture

Class Term

  • java.lang.Object
    • architecture.Term
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Term
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Object describes a term containing more terms and/or atoms. A term can be composed of 0-3 subterms.
    See Also:
